OL,3,CTwo teenagers appear in court over
OL,4,Calleged Barry murder
OL,6,FTwo teenagers accused of the murder of
OL,7,Fa 38-year-old man in Barry have
OL,8,Fappeared in court.
OL,10,FThe defendants - who are aged 16 and
OL,11,F17 and cannot legally be named because
OL,12,Fof their age - are accused of killing
OL,13,FKamran Aman a week ago.
OL,15,FSouth Wales Police said officers were
OL,16,Fcalled to reports of a stabbing on
OL,17,FBarry Road just before midnight on
OL,18,FMonday, 30 June.
