OL,3,CTwo teenagers appear in court over
OL,4,Calleged Barry murder
OL,6,FThe youths accused of Mr Aman's murder
OL,7,Fappeared before Cardiff Crown Court
OL,8,Fvia video link from separate youth
OL,9,Fdetention centres on Monday, 7 July.
OL,11,FDressed in a grey sweater, the first
OL,12,Fdefendant spoke only to confirm his
OL,13,Fname and address. At one point, he
OL,14,Fburied his face in his arms.
OL,16,FThe 16-year-old defendant, dressed in
OL,17,Fa black T-shirt, also spoke only to
OL,18,Fconfirm his name and address.
OL,20,FMembers of Mr Aman's family were in
OL,21,Fcourt and appeared tearful.
