OL,6,FJudge Tracey Lloyd-Clarke, the
OL,7,FRecorder of Cardiff, told the
OL,8,Fdefendants that a further hearing
OL,9,Fwould take place in August, with a
OL,10,Fprovisional trial date set for
OL,11,FNovember 17.
OL,13,FPolice have previously said both
OL,14,Fdefendants are from Llantwit Major, in
OL,15,Fthe Vale of Glamorgan.
OL,17,FThe family of Mr Aman described him as
OL,18,Fas "loving" father of one and a
OL,19,F"devoted" husband.
