OL,6,FIn a statement issued via police, Mr
OL,7,FAman's family said: "It was with
OL,8,Fprofound sorrow and heavy hearts that
OL,9,Fwe mourn the tragic loss of Kamran.
OL,11,F"As we grieve this unimaginable loss,
OL,12,Fwe also honour and celebrate the life
OL,13,Fhe lived and the impact he made."
OL,15,F"May his memory be a blessing."
